# Stuff and Things

So What is stuff exactly? The [RDF](https://www.w3.org/RDF/) folks organize stuff by using simple three term statements. If you want facts you can use 4 so that the time/context is also stated. Check out the presentation below to get a better sense of it. You'll have to use the arrows at the top of the light box to move between slides.
